{
  "stem": "1343.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the German took out his pistol and he said-- [LAUGHS] pointed it at the lieutenant-- this was a German private first class, maybe-- [LAUGHS] and said, tell him-- tell the Jew-- that if he ever touches you again in front of me, I will shoot him.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So anyhow, this is how-- and I have to say that these Germans were not SS.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were the Wehrmacht, the regular army Germans, who did not know about these stories about the Jews have to be handled like animals.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So from that point on, really, the Hungarians were taking us out, taking back, but they gave it back to us in our own circle, of course.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So anyhow, they were asking for different type of treatment, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Schneiders-- ?] these tailors, they went into the German headquarters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They worked there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had a good job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They asked for clerks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were a couple of news reporters, so they became the Germans' clerks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they asked for gardeners, so that was tailor-made for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I became their gardener.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I took my uncle with me and a couple other guys.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So for that period of six months while I was there, I had a lot of very good times in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were able to being back with my uncle from the Germans raw potatoes, flour that my uncle, [NON-ENGLISH], set up a kosher kitchen.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were six or seven of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We ate nothing but kosher, including me in the beginning, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so this is--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Around them, in their headquarters-- this was from June until November-- I was planting flowers, cutting rose bushes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had some fruit trees I took care of.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
